node.text:
Today I transformed into Anna from the new Frozen 2 movie, using a bunch of products from the new @colourpopcosmetics Anna Collection! Absolutely love the Disney collections from Colourpop so I’m so excited to be partnering with them for the new Frozen 2 one!

You can also use code ABBY for $$$ off your @colourpopcosmetics purchase! 
#ad #frozen2andcolourpop #colourpop

Song: @bbnomula pop song
